2. In this Act-                                                    Interpreta-
                                                                     tion.
    “commencement of this Act” means 16th September,
        1963;
    “the Federation” means the Federation called
        Malaysia after the federation of the new States
        with States forming the Federation of Malaya;
    “Minister” means the Minister responsible for external
        affairs;
    “the new States” means North Borneo, Sarawak and
        Singapore;
    “Parliament” means the Parliament of Jamaica.
